sources.title: Stealin Aint Honest (1940)
sources.description: Olive has a map that shows the location of her secret gold mine, but while she's showing it to Popeye, claim jumper Bluto photographs it and gets there first. Watch on RetroFlix:Â  https://retroflix.org/stealin-aint-honest-1940/

metadata.Plot: Popeye and Olive are on their way to an island that has a secret gold mine, but Bluto has photographed their map and disabled their boat. However, Popeye overcomes Bluto's dastardly deed by propelling the boat to the island using an egg-beater. Once there, Popeye's supply of spinach enables him to beat all of Bluto's obstacles.
metadata.Actors: Margie Hines, Jack Mercer, Tedd Pierce
